properties.property: Police Officer: Don't shoot! We have injured! Oh you're OSAC! We've heard about you! We need to get these people out of the city now, before Chaos overwhelms us!

???: We see the progress you're making over there, here's a bit of intel. Chaos prefers to scorch police officers instead of making them corrupt. This info was pretty interesting to us also. Think you can also do a favor for us? Destroy the Chaos Tank to the Northwest of the city entrance, it's been a pain for too long.

property.value: Chaos Intercom: Abandon your homes! Abandon your government! Abandon all hope! We have your precious mayor and if we don't get 500 soldiers at the town hall, we are shooting him!

properties.property: Chaos has secured this town for their own needs, we are to move in and secure civilians from their clutches. There are also reports of gunfire from the city, perhaps investigate the eastern side of the city.

property.name: globalMessage
property.value: TMU Soldier: Who are you?! Doesn't matter, help us deal with these scum!

properties.property: ???: That chopper was top secret military equipment and we don't know if we can trust you yet, so... I don't think we'll be giving you anything for the time being, only info... We prefer to not expose ourselves too much... Especially after the Bloody March.

???: Thanks for dealing with that Death Tank, now I know you want a reward but please head west of your base... That Death Tank was targeted by us for a reason, it shot down one of our aircraft. Head to the helicopter and destroy it, then you'll get your reward...

LOCATION: OUTSIDE BOISE CITY TIME OF DAY: 1200 HOURS OBJECTIVE: SECURE BOISE FROM CHAOS OCCUPATION DETAILS: BOISE HAS BEEN SEIZED BY CHAOS AND THE TOWN RECENTLY PUT OUT A DISTRESS SIGNAL ASKING FOR LIBERATION. TRY TO SECURE CIVILIANS AND DELIVER THEM TO THE PROVIDED BUILDING, THEY'LL FOLLOW OSAC INFANTRYMEN OR ANY OFFICERS WE FIND STILL FIGHTING OFF CHAOS.

???: Hey you, I see your soldiers moving into town like your the destined heroes of the place, you're OSAC right? Well we're trying to retake this part of the country from Chaos, so please.... Oh, I see General. Well congratulations looks like you'll be doing some errands for us. Who am I? Well that question won't be getting answered any time soon because of the Bloody March. I need you to first rescue 10 of our people, destroy one of the Death tanks and destroy one of our helicopter wrecks, deal?
